    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's a good start. could you add a little more warmth to it though? like, we really liked them and i want them to feel like they are still on our radar for future openings, but i don't want it to sound fake or like we're wasting their time. maybe something about how we'll keep their info on file?",
